description: The first coronavirus testing laboratory on the Isle of Man is expected to deliver results in 24 hours.
title: Coronavirus: New Manx laboratory 'will half wait for test results'
title_page: Coronavirus: New Manx laboratory 'will half wait for test results' - BBC News
maintext: The facility, which began work on Monday, is expected to give results within 24 hours rather than a previous wait time of two to three days.
